### Image Requirements:
- **Size**: 400x400px recommended (square aspect ratio)
- **Format**: JPG or PNG
- **File size**: Under 500KB for web optimization
- **Style**: Professional headshots with clean backgrounds preferred

Images will automatically appear on the team page once placed in this folder with the correct filename.
